OL,4,Cout of money over budget delay
OL,6,FThe UUP has argued that the budget
OL,7,Fshould be delayed to factor in further
OL,8,Ffunds that will be available to
OL,9,FStormont in the June monitoring round
OL,10,F` part of the in-year process of
OL,11,Freallocating returned or new money to
OL,12,Fdepartments.
OL,14,FHealth Minister Mr Swann has warned
OL,15,Fthat the budget allocation for his
OL,16,Fdepartment will inflict "irreparable"
OL,17,Fdamage on Northern Ireland's health
OL,18,Fservice.
