OL,3,CMinister warns departments could run
OL,4,Cout of money over budget delay
OL,6,FThe health service has been allocated
OL,7,Fmore than half of the Executive's
OL,8,F#14.5 billion resource budget.
OL,10,FMinisterial deliberations last month
OL,11,Ffocused on #1 billion of uncommitted
OL,12,Ffunds. Mr Swann had bid for all that
OL,13,Fmoney but ultimately received just
OL,14,Fover #500 million.
OL,16,FThe minister is due to resign from
OL,17,Fthis role on Tuesday evening in a move
OL,18,Funrelated to the budget. His is
OL,19,Fstepping down to focus on running in
OL,20,Fthe Westminster election.
