OL,3,CMinister warns departments could run
OL,4,Cout of money over budget delay
OL,6,FHe is to be replaced by former UUP
OL,7,Fleader Mike Nesbitt.
OL,9,FAhead of the Assembly debate on the
OL,10,Fbudget, Mr Swann warned fellow
OL,11,FExecutive ministers that no UUP
OL,12,Fminister would introduce the cost-
OL,13,Fsaving measures required to balance
OL,14,Fthe department's budget.
OL,16,FThat raises the prospect of Mr Nesbitt
OL,17,Foverspending the departmental budget
OL,18,Fwhen he takes over the role.
