OL,3,CMinister warns departments could run
OL,4,Cout of money over budget delay
OL,6,FAddressing the Assembly at the outset
OL,7,Fof the debate, Ms Archibald said the
OL,8,FExecutive was in line to receive
OL,9,F"significant" extra funding from the
OL,10,FTreasury in-year. But she said the
OL,11,Ftimeline for receiving confirmation on
OL,12,Fthe amount had been pushed back the
OL,13,FGeneral Election had been called.
OL,15,F"I am aware that some believe that
OL,16,Fthis budget should be delayed to allow
OL,17,Fthese additional allocations to be
OL,18,Fincluded," she said.
OL,20,F"However, Assembly approval of this
OL,21,Fbudget cannot be delayed.
