OL,6,FMs Archibald said if she was unable to
OL,7,Fbring the formal Budget Bill to the
OL,8,FAssembly before the summer recess then
OL,9,Fdepartments may reach the limit of the
OL,10,Fcash they have been authorised to
OL,11,Fspend pending the Bill's passage.
OL,13,F"I cannot contemplate a situation
OL,14,Fwhere departments could be unable to
OL,15,Faccess cash to deliver services," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
