OL,6,FMs Archibald also warned that a
OL,7,FTreasury pledge to write off a
OL,8,F#559million debt, on the condition
OL,9,Fthat Stormont puts its finances on a
OL,10,Fmore sustainable basis, could be
OL,11,Fwithdrawn if the Executive overspent
OL,12,Fits budget.
OL,14,F"If a balanced budget is not agreed,
OL,15,Fthe write-off of #559m provided in the
OL,16,Ffinancial package is potentially at
OL,17,Frisk," she said.
