OL,6,FHe added: "Sinn Fein, the DUP and
OL,7,FAlliance would have you vote for a
OL,8,Fbudget that could in all probability
OL,9,Fhave an extra quarter of a million
OL,10,Fpounds to be allocated in less than 30
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,F"How can any self-respecting MLA
